<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Sparrow</strong></span> is back in New York City and reading a lot. He recommends <em>Death Comes for the Archbishop</em> by Willa Cather, <em>Exile and the Kingdom</em> by Camus and &ldquo;Couple Attacked by Talking Bear&rdquo; (article, <em>National Enquirer</em>, August 6, 1985).</p><a href="/contributors/sparrow" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
